flowchart TD
    Start([Mulai Penelitian]) --> Problem[Identifikasi Masalah<br/>fragmentasi sistem PMS<br/>hotel kecil-menengah,<br/>tidak ada chatbot LLM native]

    Problem --> Lit[Studi Literatur<br/>PMS, LLM, Chatbot,<br/>UI/UX, HCI, Agile]

    Lit --> Compare[Analisis Komparatif<br/>Oracle OPERA, Cloudbeds,<br/>Little Hotelier]

    Compare --> Gap[Identifikasi Gap<br/>tidak ada PMS terjangkau<br/>+ chatbot LLM native<br/>untuk hotel kecil Indonesia]

    Gap --> Need[Analisis Kebutuhan<br/>case study hotel teman<br/>+ wawancara stakeholder]

    Need --> Design[Perancangan Sistem<br/>UML: Use Case, Class,<br/>Sequence, Activity, ERD<br/>+ UI wireframe]

    Design --> Stack[Pemilihan Tech Stack<br/>Next.js 16, TypeScript,<br/>Supabase PostgreSQL,<br/>Gemini 2.5 Flash via AI SDK]

    Stack --> Implement[Implementasi Iteratif<br/>Agile Scrum<br/>2-minggu sprint cycle]

    Implement --> Modules[13 Modul Operasional<br/>Auth, Dashboard, Rooms,<br/>Occupancy, Guests, Billing,<br/>HK, Inventory, Chatbot, dst]

    Modules --> Testing[Pengujian Sistem<br/>Black Box 34 skenario<br/>9 modul utama]

    Testing --> UAT[User Acceptance Testing<br/>Likert 1-5<br/>Staf n=10, Tamu n=20]

    UAT --> Eval[Evaluasi Tambahan<br/>5 Faktor Manusia Terukur<br/>8 Aturan Emas Shneiderman<br/>SUS Brooke 1996]

    Eval --> Analysis[Analisis & Pembahasan<br/>vs Rumusan Masalah]

    Analysis --> Conclusion[Simpulan & Saran<br/>+ Limitasi single-case<br/>+ Future work mobile,<br/>OTA integration, RAG]

    Conclusion --> End([Selesai])

